# Python Scripting Notes

## 1. Check Python Version

python3 --version

---

## 2. Create Python Script

touch script.py

Run:
python3 script.py

---

## 3. Basic Python Script

print("Hello Lucy")

---

## 4. Variables

name = "Lucy"
print(name)

---

## 5. User Input

user = input("Enter your name: ")
print("Hello", user)

---

## 6. If Statement

if user == "Lucy":
    print("Welcome back!")
